n.Lars Wilhelmer zeigt: Im Zeitalter von Globalisierung und Mobilität bieten diese Orte, verschmolzen zu hyperkulturellen Transit-Räumen, das, was konventionelle Orte längst nicht mehr bieten können - einen Halt, eine Zuflucht.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 0aAirports in literature. 0aGerman literaturex20th centuryxHistory and criticism. 0aGerman literaturexHistory and criticism. 0aGerman literaturey20th centuryxHistory and criticism. 0aHarbors in literature. 0aHotels in literature. 0aLiteraturexThemes, motives. 0aRailroad storiesxHistory and criticism. 0aTravelers in literature. 0aTravelers' writingsxHistory and criticism. 4aAllgemeine Literaturwissenschaft. 4aGermanistik. 4aLiteratur. 4aLiteraturwissenschaft. 4aModerne. 4aOrt. 4aRaum. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / European / German.2bisacsh  aGeneral Literature Studies.  aGerman Literature.  aLiterary Studies.  aLiterature.  aModernity.  aPlace.  aSpace.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2015z978311070098508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2015z9783110439687oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Literary, Cultural and Area Studies 2015z9783110438673oZDB-23-DKU08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Complete eBook Package 2014-2016z9783110489842oZDB-23-TGP40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/transcript.9783839429990zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839429990423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783839429990/original  a978-3-11-070098-5  DG Plus eBook-Package 2015b2015  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_LT  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGGb2015  aZDB-23-